<p><strong>所属设施：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Site-CN-█</span> EXC-Site-CN-10（特外站点十号）</p>
<p><strong>职务：</strong>异常生物学高级研究员，[应急]后勤技术员</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;描述：[需权限]</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
